labels.label: Query the db for anything with a change later than the latest"last_change"
For each row returned, set an "_id" so we can do Upsert when ingesting data
Find the latest "last_change" date in ES

entry.value: SELECT concat( labReport.observation_uid,',', labReport.local_id,',', labReport.local_id, ',', labReport.subject_entity_uid, ',', type_cd,',', act_uid) id, ( SELECT Max(v) FROM ( VALUES(person_last_chg_time), (observation_last_chg_time), (act_id_last_chg_time), (participation_last_chg_time)) AS value (v)) AS last_change, labReport.* FROM ( SELECT act.class_cd class_cd, act.mood_cd mood_cd, act_id.type_desc_txt type_desc_txt, act_id.root_extension_txt root_extension_txt, observation.observation_uid observation_uid, observation.cd_desc_txt cd_desc_txt, observation2.program_jurisdiction_oid program_jurisdiction_oid, observation2.prog_area_cd program_area_cd, observation2.jurisdiction_cd jurisdiction_cd, observation.pregnant_ind_cd pregnant_ind_cd, observation.local_id local_id, observation.activity_to_time activity_to_time, observation.effective_from_time effective_from_time, observation.rpt_to_state_time rpt_to_state_time, observation.add_time add_time, observation.electronic_ind electronic_ind, observation.version_ctrl_nbr version_ctrl_nbr, observation2.record_status_cd observation_record_status_cd, observation.add_user_id add_user_id, observation.last_chg_user_id last_chg_user_id, participation.type_cd type_cd, participation.subject_class_cd subject_class_cd, participation.subject_entity_uid subject_entity_uid, act.act_uid act_uid, person.cd person_cd, person.record_status_cd person_record_status_cd, ovc.display_name display_name, participation.last_chg_time participation_last_chg_time, act_id.last_chg_time act_id_last_chg_time, person.last_chg_time person_last_chg_time, observation.last_chg_time observation_last_chg_time FROM dbo.observation JOIN dbo.act_relationship actRel ON (observation.observation_uid = actRel.source_act_uid) LEFT JOIN dbo.observation observation2 ON (observation2.observation_uid = actRel.target_act_uid) LEFT JOIN dbo.obs_value_coded ovc ON (ovc.observation_uid = actRel.source_act_uid) LEFT JOIN dbo.act act ON (act.act_uid = actRel.target_act_uid) LEFT JOIN dbo.participation participation ON (participation.act_uid = act.act_uid) LEFT JOIN dbo.act_id act_id ON (act_id.act_uid = observation.observation_uid) LEFT JOIN dbo.Person person ON (person.person_uid = participation.subject_entity_uid)) AS labReport WHERE ( SELECT Max(v) FROM ( VALUES(person_last_chg_time), (observation_last_chg_time), (act_id_last_chg_time), (participation_last_chg_time)) AS value (v)) > '${last_change}' ORDER BY last_change ASC;
